{"tid":1816763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，屯門欣田區連區選都輸埋，完全對依區死心","createTime":"2020-01-08T13:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T16:50:20.000Z","uid":276245,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5aecee02a0b461f49168addb576e25c1bfbfd1c6","tid":1816763,"uid":276245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然欣田區選輸左，但其實場仗仲未完嫁！黎緊仲有互委會依一場戰役！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">互委會有咩玩？？</span><br />\n&mdash;》可以每兩個月一次同apple姐 - 賴嘉汶瘋狂開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 任何一個邨內既事務/建設，除左要咨詢當區議員，亦要咨詢互委會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係如果大家選到互委會既，到時apple姐建議咩，大家可以全部<span style=\"color: red;\">BAN</span>哂佢！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;》可以做<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撥款</span></span>，包括撥款做邨內工程/搞社區活動。其他邨個d社區活動呢，其實大部分都係由紅底機構機構搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">根本上，互委會就係一個迷你版既區議會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黎緊欣田應該差唔多係時候選互委會，我地想搵一班欣田手足一齊諗諗計，可以點玩。大家有興趣既，就留底tg，一齊搞搞佢。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復欣田邨！佔領互委會</span></span>"},{"pid"